---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About — Ralf Tsai"
  description="About Ralf Tsai, an oceanography graduate student, environmental educator, and creator of If No Plastic."
>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="about-hero">
     <img src="/about-profile.jpg" alt="Portrait of Chun-Hung Tsai at the Institute of Oceanography" />

      <div>
        <p class="kicker">About</p>
        <h1>Sustainability, and stories that connect people with the world around them.</h1>

        <p>
          I’m Chun-Hung Tsai, also known as Ralf, from Kaohsiung, Taiwan. I studied
          Applied Chemistry at National Pingtung University, with a minor in the Applied
          Biotechnology Credit Program, and received multiple academic excellence awards during my undergraduate years.
        </p>

        <p>
          My academic path later led me across disciplines to the Institute of Oceanography
          at National Taiwan University. My academic background began in chemistry and gradually
          led me into oceanography, where I focus on environmental change. I enjoy turning
          complex scientific information into clear, meaningful stories that can be understood
          by broader audiences.
        </p>

        <p>
          Beyond research, I care deeply about environmental education. Through
          <strong>@Ifnoplastic.tw （如果無塑）</strong>, I document sustainability practices, ocean-related
          issues, vegetarian living, campus observations, and small actions that can reconnect
          people with the environment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>What I Do</h2>

      <ul class="what-i-do">
        <li>
          <strong>Leadership & Collaboration</strong><br />
          I previously served as President of the Chongde Volunteer Club and Vice President
          of the Department Student Association, where I developed strengths in teamwork,
          communication, and cross-disciplinary coordination.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Research & Professional Experience</strong><br />
          I have interned in both NGO and industry settings, including work related to local
          revitalization and an internship at TCI Co., Ltd., which strengthened my ability
          to connect academic research with real-world practice.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>International Engagement</strong><br />
          I currently serve as a board member of the Sakura Science Program, a science exchange
          initiative under Japan Science and Technology Agency (JST).
        </li>
      </ul>

      <figure class="feature-image">
        <img src="/altruism-award.jpg" alt="Ralf Tsai receiving an award at National Taiwan University commencement" />
        <figcaption>
          Honored with the Altruism Award of the College of Science at National Taiwan University upon graduation.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>My Interests</h2>

      <p>
        I’m drawn to the kinds of experiences that make life feel observant, reflective, and alive.
        I enjoy photography, travel, good food, reading, and writing—especially Chinese prose.
        In daily life, I also enjoy swimming and yoga, and recently I’ve been learning to skateboard.
      </p>

      <p>
        Many of the things I love have one thing in common: they help me notice the world more carefully.
        Whether it is through a camera lens, a quiet paragraph, a journey to a new place, or the rhythm
        of movement in water, I value moments that slow me down and bring me closer to what is real.
      </p>

      <figure class="feature-image">
        <img src="/sea.jpg" alt="The sea near dusk" />
        <figcaption>
          My favorite moment is the sea just before evening—quiet, open, and full of space to think.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    display: grid;
    gap: 64px;
  }

  .about-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: start;
  }

.about-hero img {
  /* About 頁照片尺寸：想更大就改這兩個 */
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;

  /* cover = 裁切成固定比例；適合頭像與人物照 */
  object-fit: cover;

  /* 調整裁切位置：
     center = 中央
     top = 臉部偏上時可用
     50% 35% = 更精準控制水平/垂直位置 */
  object-position: center;

  /* 圓角方形風格，像質感個人網站 */
  border-radius: 34px;

  border: 5px solid white;
  box-shadow: 0 22px 52px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.14);
}

  .kicker {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #6c88ad;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    color: #1a2744;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    color: #1a2744;
    font-size: 26px;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.72);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  strong {
    color: #1a2744;
  }

  .section {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .what-i-do {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    color: rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.72);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .what-i-do li::marker {
    color: #6c88ad;
  }

  .feature-image {
    margin: 14px 0 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .feature-image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 26px;
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid rgba(168, 200, 240, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 46px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.08);
  }

  figcaption {
    color: rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.52);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 720px) {
    .about-hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .about-hero img {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(34px, 10vw, 30px);
    }

    p,
    .what-i-do {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }
</style>